node.text:
There is no better way to start September than to start it with a new @Skeletonconceptofficial. And gosh did they deliver!
 
Let us introduce you to the #Maldonado Concept timepiece, a special design made for the @F1 Venezuelan racing driver, @pastormaldo - Pastor Maldonado.
This spectacular timepiece pushes the limits and the codes of the Daytona 116520 furthermore, thanks to its skeletonized design and the stunning and very elegant blue-ish & grey palette tones used on the dial. The bezel - in 5 grade Titanium (the highest level of quality for this material)  gives it a smooth and minimalist aspect.
 
We can’t quite put our finger on it? Is it the combination of the high standard “bleu horloger” with the matte Oyster steel bracelet, the sharp handmade bevelling of the movement or something else entirely - but this timepiece definitely has something more than the others. It unequivocally reminds us of racing cars and  Formula One.
 
A demonstration of the finest watchmaking and haute horology.
 
WE LOVE IT.
_________________________________

The personalization of the watches are carried out meticulously while staying true to the essence of the original brand manufacturers. Skeleton Concept assures the integrity of the work and modifications made on behalf of its clients and their timepieces. Any and all the customizations made are for the personal and private use of the owners only.

node.text:
The @waldanwatches Pastel Edition Capsule Collection is now available for sale! Featuring three meticulously designed new models; Sky Blue (ref. 0196BL), Blush Pink (ref. 0196P) and Canary Yellow (ref. 0196C), these limited edition watches are limited to 300 pcs. 

Crafted with the signature details that make a watch a Waldan, these models offer a more vibrant color way into the Heritage collection. All watches are individually hand assembled in the United States, certified and tested under a proprietary zero defect protocol and are powered by the jeweled and all-metal, American Made “Ameriquartz” cal. 70200 movement that is fully serviceable and warrantied for 5 years. 

Available for sale now at waldanwatches.com, free shipping available for domestic orders.
